---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<style is:global>
  .tc-hero-section { padding: 80px 24px 60px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .tc-hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: center; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .tc-stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .tc-hero-img { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; opacity: 0.15; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
  .tc-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .el-two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .el-econ-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; align-items: center; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tc-hero-section { padding: 48px 20px 48px !important; }
    .tc-hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 36px !important; }
    .tc-stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important; gap: 12px !important; }
    .el-two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 28px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; }
    .el-econ-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 24px !important; }
  }
</style>

<Layout title="For Transport Companies" description="Join the Tow It driver network. Get confirmed vehicle transport jobs sent straight to your WhatsApp. No bidding, no platforms, no wasted time. Guaranteed payment within 7 days.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="tc-hero-section" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#080C14 0%,#0E1421 100%);">
    <img src="/images/driver-whatsapp-job.jpg" alt="" class="tc-hero-img" />
    <div class="tc-hero-grid">
      <div class="tc-hero-content">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(0,232,143,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.2);border-radius:9999px;padding:6px 14px;margin-bottom:20px;">
          <span style="color:#00E88F;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">For Transport Companies</span>
        </div>
        <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:900;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:20px;">Get paid jobs straight to your WhatsApp ‚Äî including on your way home.</h1>
        <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;">Stop wasting time bidding on other platforms for jobs that go to the cheapest quote. Join the Tow It network and receive confirmed, fairly-priced vehicle transport jobs delivered directly to your phone ‚Äî including smart <strong style="color:#00E88F;">Empty Leg jobs</strong> that turn your return journey into more revenue.</p>
        <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:32px;">You accept or decline from WhatsApp. The job details, collection address, and delivery point all come pre-packaged. Payment is guaranteed within 7 days of delivery. It's the way vehicle transport should work.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;">
          <a href="#register" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#00E88F;color:#080C14;font-weight:700;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:9999px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.95rem;">
            Apply to Join the Network
          </a>
          <a href="#how-it-works" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border:1px solid #1A2540;color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:9999px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.95rem;">
            How It Works for Drivers
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tc-stats-grid tc-hero-content">
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:#00E88F;margin-bottom:6px;">7 days</div>
          <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.85rem;">Guaranteed payment</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:#00C2FF;margin-bottom:6px;">¬£0</div>
          <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.85rem;">Cost to join</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:#FF6B2B;margin-bottom:6px;">500+</div>
          <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.85rem;">Active drivers in network</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:2px solid #00E88F;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:#00E88F;margin-bottom:6px;">No bids</div>
          <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.85rem;">Fixed price every time</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,232,143,0.12),rgba(0,194,255,0.08));border:1px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;grid-column:1/-1;margin-top:4px;">
        <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px;">üîÅ Empty Leg Intelligence</div>
        <div style="color:#ffffff;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.5;">We proactively find you a job <em>on the way home</em> ‚Äî so you earn twice, not once.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS FOR DRIVERS -->
  <section id="how-it-works" style="padding:80px 24px;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem);font-weight:800;color:#ffffff;margin-bottom:12px;">How it works for you</h2>
      <p style="color:#8B96A8;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7;">Once you're verified and in the network, getting work is effortless.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:40px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;">
      <img src="/images/transport-fleet.jpg" alt="Row of professional car transporter trucks at sunset" style="width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;" />
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;">
      <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:start;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:#00E88F;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#080C14;flex-shrink:0;">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">Job appears in your WhatsApp</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">When a customer books a job in your area that matches your vehicle capability, you'll receive a WhatsApp message from Tow It with the full job details: vehicle type, collection point, delivery point, distance, date/time window, and confirmed payment amount. No vague descriptions, no guessing what's involved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:start;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:#00C2FF;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#080C14;flex-shrink:0;">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">Accept or decline ‚Äî your choice</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">Reply YES to accept the job, or DECLINE if it doesn't work for you. There's no pressure and no penalty for declining ‚Äî we understand transport companies have complex schedules. The job will be offered to the next suitable driver in the network if you decline.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:start;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:#FF6B2B;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#ffffff;flex-shrink:0;">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">Collect and deliver</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">Contact the collection point, pick up the vehicle, carry out the condition check via our driver app (takes 2 minutes ‚Äî just photos and a sign-off), and deliver to the destination. Update your status via WhatsApp as you go ‚Äî our AI handles the customer communications automatically.</p>
          <img src="/images/driver-loading.jpg" alt="Professional driver carefully loading luxury car onto transporter" style="width:100%;max-width:480px;height:auto;border-radius:10px;margin-top:16px;display:block;" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:start;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:#00E88F;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#080C14;flex-shrink:0;">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">Get paid within 7 days</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">Once delivery is confirmed, payment is processed automatically within 7 days ‚Äî straight to your bank account. No chasing invoices, no waiting 60 days, no excuses. Our drivers tell us the prompt, guaranteed payment is the single biggest benefit of working with Tow It.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EMPTY LEG INTELLIGENCE -->
  <section style="padding:80px 24px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#060A12 0%,#0A1020 60%,#080C14 100%);border-top:2px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.2);border-bottom:2px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.2);position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
    <div style="position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-80px;width:400px;height:400px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,232,143,0.07) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:60px;">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(0,232,143,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.3);border-radius:9999px;padding:8px 18px;margin-bottom:20px;">
          <span style="color:#00E88F;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;">üîÅ Our Biggest Partner Benefit</span>
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3.5vw,2.75rem);font-weight:900;color:#ffffff;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.15;">Stop driving home empty.<br><span style="color:#00E88F;">We fill your return journey.</span></h2>
        <p style="color:#8B96A8;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.8;font-size:1.05rem;">Every transport company knows the problem: you've just delivered a vehicle and you're heading home with an empty trailer. That return journey costs you fuel, time, and wear ‚Äî but earns you nothing. Tow It fixes this with smart Empty Leg matching.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Two-column layout: image + explanation -->
      <div class="el-two-col">
        <div>
          <img src="/images/empty-leg-route.jpg" alt="AI route map showing empty leg job matching for car transporter return journey" style="width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:20px;display:block;border:2px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.2);box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:clamp(1.25rem,2.5vw,1.75rem);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.3;">We know where you are. So we find you work nearby.</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px;">When you complete a job and confirm delivery via WhatsApp, our AI immediately checks your current location against all pending customer requests in the area. If there's a vehicle that needs moving near your delivery point ‚Äî on or close to your route home ‚Äî we reach out to you directly.</p>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:28px;">The job is offered to you at a preferential rate ‚Äî slightly below our standard price to make it an easy yes for the customer too. But here's the maths: <strong style="color:#ffffff;">something is always better than nothing.</strong> Fuel costs are already sunk. Any revenue on the way home is pure profit margin.</p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
              <div style="width:8px;height:8px;background:#00E88F;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
              <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:0.9rem;">You've already done the drive ‚Äî fuel is a sunk cost</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
              <div style="width:8px;height:8px;background:#00E88F;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
              <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:0.9rem;">Every pound earned on the return is near-pure profit</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
              <div style="width:8px;height:8px;background:#00E88F;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
              <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:0.9rem;">You choose ‚Äî accept or decline in one WhatsApp reply</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
              <div style="width:8px;height:8px;background:#00E88F;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
              <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:0.9rem;">No extra admin ‚Äî payment processed same as any other job</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Before/After comparison image -->
      <div style="margin-bottom:64px;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #1A2540;">
        <img src="/images/empty-leg-comparison.jpg" alt="Comparison showing empty return journey vs profitable empty leg job with Tow It" style="width:100%;max-height:360px;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
      </div>

      <!-- How it actually works - 3 steps -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2.5vw,1.6rem);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;">How Empty Leg matching works</h3>
        <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;">Three steps. Completely automatic. No extra effort from you.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:24px;margin-bottom:56px;">
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:32px;text-align:center;position:relative;">
          <div style="width:56px;height:56px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00E88F,#00C2FF);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#080C14;font-size:1.2rem;margin:0 auto 20px;">1</div>
          <h4 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:1rem;">You confirm delivery</h4>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.7;">You complete your job and confirm delivery via WhatsApp as normal. Our AI logs your current location ‚Äî the delivery point ‚Äî in real time.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:32px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="width:56px;height:56px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00C2FF,#7B5FFF);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#ffffff;font-size:1.2rem;margin:0 auto 20px;">2</div>
          <h4 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:1rem;">We scan for nearby jobs</h4>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.7;">Instantly, our system checks all pending customer requests within a smart radius of your location ‚Äî prioritising anything that's on or near your homeward route and matched to your vehicle type.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:32px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="width:56px;height:56px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FF6B2B,#FF3D71);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;color:#ffffff;font-size:1.2rem;margin:0 auto 20px;">3</div>
          <h4 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:1rem;">We WhatsApp you a job offer</h4>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.7;">If there's a match, you'll receive a WhatsApp message with full details and a slightly reduced price. Reply YES to accept and collect, or DECLINE if it doesn't work for you ‚Äî no pressure, no penalty.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The economics box -->
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#141C2E,#0E1421);border:1px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.25);border-radius:20px;padding:40px;" class="el-econ-grid">
        <div>
          <h3 style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px;">The economics are simple</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px;">Let's say your standard job rate for a 60-mile delivery is ¬£120. On an empty leg, we might offer you ¬£85 for a 40-mile pickup on your way home. That's ¬£85 more than the ¬£0 you'd earn driving back empty ‚Äî at barely any additional cost to you.</p>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;line-height:1.8;">For a full-time operator doing 10 jobs a week, capturing even 3‚Äì4 empty leg jobs per week at an average of ¬£80 adds <strong style="color:#ffffff;">¬£960‚Äì¬£1,280 per month in near-pure profit</strong>. That's the kind of number that changes a business.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;">
          <div style="background:#080C14;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;">
            <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:8px;">Without Empty Leg</div>
            <div style="color:#FF3D71;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:4px;">¬£0</div>
            <div style="color:#4A5568;font-size:0.8rem;">earned on return journey</div>
          </div>
          <div style="background:#080C14;border:1px solid rgba(0,232,143,0.2);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;">
            <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:8px;">With Tow It Empty Leg</div>
            <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:4px;">¬£60‚Äì¬£120</div>
            <div style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.8rem;">extra per return journey ‚Äî near-pure profit</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VETTING PROCESS -->
  <section style="padding:0 24px 80px;background:#0E1421;border-top:1px solid #1A2540;border-bottom:1px solid #1A2540;padding-top:80px;padding-bottom:80px;">
    <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px;">
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem);font-weight:800;color:#ffffff;margin-bottom:12px;">What we check before you join</h2>
        <p style="color:#8B96A8;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7;">Our customers trust us with their vehicles. So we take the quality of our network seriously. Here's what we verify before a transport company can receive any jobs.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom:40px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;">
        <img src="/images/driver-vetting.jpg" alt="Professional vetting and background check documents" style="width:100%;max-height:280px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;" />
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:24px;">
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
          <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:12px;">‚úì</div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">Motor Trade Insurance</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">Valid motor trade insurance covering the collection and delivery of third-party vehicles. We check the certificate directly and verify it's in date. Annual re-verification required.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
          <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:12px;">‚úì</div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">Goods in Transit Cover</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">Appropriate goods-in-transit insurance covering the value of vehicles in your care during transport. Minimum coverage levels depend on the vehicle tier you want to handle.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
          <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:12px;">‚úì</div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">Operator Licence (if applicable)</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">For transport companies operating vehicles over 3.5 tonnes or running multiple vehicles for hire or reward, a valid Operator Licence from the DVSA is required. We check DVSA records directly.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
          <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:12px;">‚úì</div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">Identity Verification</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">We verify the identity of the individual or company director registering. This is a standard KYC check to ensure we know who we're working with and prevent fraudulent accounts.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
          <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:12px;">‚úì</div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">Equipment Check</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">We need to understand what vehicle types you can handle ‚Äî open transporter, enclosed, flatbed recovery, motorcycle, etc. This ensures we match the right jobs to the right equipment every time.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#141C2E;border:1px solid #1A2540;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
          <div style="color:#00E88F;font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:12px;">‚úì</div>
          <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">References or Reviews</h3>
          <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">New applicants with no existing Tow It track record are asked to provide two trade references or demonstrate an existing verified review history on a third-party platform. Experienced, reputable companies are onboarded faster.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

